<section class="main-container container">
  <div class="main-content">
    <h1 class="main-title">UIPlayground - is a UI library that allows you to present and demonstrate any other library and your custom components.</h1>
    <div class="main-desc">
      <p>With the help of UIP components we allow you to 'play' with a component.</p>
      <p>You can choose from the variety of component's templates, play with the component's settings or even change its
        markup!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <uip-root editor-collapsed>
    <script type="text/html" uip-snippet label="Logo">
      <div class="logo-content gray-clr">
        <a class="get-started" href="{{ '/general/getting-started/' | url }}">
          <span>Get Started with</span>
          <div>
            <svg width="100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 268 268">
              <circle cx="135" cy="134" r="116" fill="none" stroke-width="10"/>
